            <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
            <p>
                At KhumaloCraft Emporium, we are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring the security of your personal information. 
                This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard the information you provide to us through our website.
            </p>

            <p><b>Information We Collect</b></p>
                <p>
